10. Historical compliance tracking
    

---

# Contributor Recognition

All accepted contributions are acknowledged through Git history.

Significant architectural contributions may also be recognized in project release notes and documentation.

---

# Final Note

SentinelGRC is intended to be a maintainable, extensible, and vendor-neutral compliance automation framework. Every contribution should strengthen that objective by emphasizing modular design, reusable technical evidence collection, and data-driven framework mappings over framework-specific implementations.
